		"name": "Questionnaire System — PHQ-9 / GAD-7 / DES-11",
		"description": "Separate POST and GET endpoints for PHQ-9 (depression), GAD-7 (anxiety), and DES-11 (dissociation). Users can submit multiple times. Each submission is stored independently.",
